利佐因前服装助理的骚扰诉讼被驳回https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-dismissed-from-harassment-lawsuit-by-former-wardrobe-assistant-3819796?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lizzo-dismissed-from-harassment-lawsuit-作者：前衣橱助理Liberty DunworthFri, 06 Dec 2024 16:22:16 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3819796 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lizzo 出席 2024 年 Met Gala" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>法官裁定歌手不能以个人身份被起诉</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-dismissed-from-harassment-lawsuit-by-former-wardrobe-assistant-3819796">利佐驳回前服装助理骚扰诉讼的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Lizzo 出席 2024 年 Met Gala" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Lizzo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzo">利佐</a>因前服装助理提起的骚扰诉讼而被驳回。</p><p>本周，她在一项关键裁决中获胜，该裁决的核心是与一名造型师正在进行的法律斗争，该造型师<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-named-in-new-bullying-and-harassment-lawsuit-from-fashion-designer-3502090">声称这位歌手在 2023 年欧洲巡演期间让她处于充满敌意的工作环境中</a>。</p><p>阿莎·丹尼尔斯于去年 9 月首次对利佐提起诉讼，指控环境使她遭受残疾歧视、性骚扰以及“种族主义和恐胖言论”。丹尼尔斯还声称，一名衣柜经理推了她，并将一个“沉重的衣架”滚到她的脚上，导致她身体受伤。</p><p>该诉讼是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-sued-by-backup-dancers-for-sexual-harassment-and-creating-hostile-work-environment-3476570">在三名前舞者对利佐提起另一起诉讼的同时</a>提起的，同样指控利佐存在性骚扰和敌对的工作环境。</p><p>当时，利佐的律师将丹尼尔斯描述为一名“心怀不满”的员工，提出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-requests-to-dismiss-meritless-harassment-and-discrimination-lawsuit-3561059">“毫无根据且淫秽”的指控。</a>这位歌手还否认了三名舞者的说法，并表示这种情况<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-clarifies-i-quit-comments-im-going-to-keep-moving-forward-3612352">让她考虑退出音乐界</a>。</p><p>现在，洛杉矶的一名联邦法官裁定丹尼尔斯没有资格起诉这位“Good As Hell”歌手。 </p><figure id="attachment_3561294" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3561294" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3561294" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Lizzo 于 2023 年 7 月 26 日在新西兰奥克兰 Spark Arena 表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Lizzo-performs@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3561294" class="wp-caption-text"> Lizzo 于 2023 年 7 月 26 日在新西兰奥克兰 Spark Arena 表演。图片来源：Dave Simpson/WireImage/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/lizzo-dismissed-harassment-lawsuit-wardrobe-assistant-1235194368/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《滚石》</em></a>报道，地区法官费尔南多·L·安内尔·罗查 (Fernando L. Aenlle-Rocha) 表示，在确认歌手的巡演和工资公司是她的雇主后，不能以个人身份起诉利佐。所有七项诉讼理由均已被驳回，丹尼尔斯被告知她不能再次尝试起诉。</p><p>该媒体还报道称，尽管 Big Grrrl Big Touring Inc. 仍是被告，但该歌手的巡演经理 Carlina Gugliotta 已脱离诉讼。</p><p> “利佐的公司没有被解雇，”丹尼尔斯的律师罗恩·赞布拉诺在一份新的声明中告诉<em>RS</em> 。 “关于 Lizzo 的公司的诉讼仍然存在……Lizzo 和她的巡演经理仍将在此事中被罢黜。”</p><p>另据悉，利佐的代表律师尚未回应置评请求。</p><p>这是一个发展的故事。</p><p>至于三名舞者提起的诉讼，去年一月的一项裁决显示，法官驳回了案件的部分内容，但允许案件继续进行。状态会议定于一月份举行。</p><p>早在十月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-retracts-gap-year-comment-its-a-grind-year-3803160">利佐就收回了之前关于她要休“间隔年”的言论，</a>并表示：“我一直在工作、工作、工作。你可能看不到我，但我一直在工作。这不是间隔年，而是苦苦挣扎的一年。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-dismissed-from-harassment-lawsuit-by-former-wardrobe-assistant-3819796">利佐驳回前服装助理骚扰诉讼的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Alice Cooper 和 Slash 合作创作摩托车主题儿童歌曲“Freewheelin” https://www.nme.com/news/music/alice-cooper-and-slash-team-up-for-motorcycle-themed-kids-song-freewheelin-3819775?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=alice-cooper-和-slash-team-up-摩托车主题儿童歌曲-freewheelinAnagricel Duran Fri, 06 Dec 2024 16:05:50 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3819775 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Alice Cooper 和 Slash，伦敦，2010 年 11 月 10 日。（摄影：Mick Hutson/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌收录在格莱美提名的儿童摇滚专辑“Solid Rock Revival”中</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alice-cooper-and-slash-team-up-for-motorcycle-themed-kids-song-freewheelin-3819775">Alice Cooper 和 Slash 合作创作的摩托车主题儿童歌曲“Freewheelin”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Alice Cooper 和 Slash，伦敦，2010 年 11 月 10 日。（摄影：Mick Hutson/Redferns）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Alice-Cooper-and-Slash-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Alice-Cooper">Alice Cooper</a> 、他的女儿 Calico 和<a href="/artists/Slash">Slash</a>合作创作了摩托车主题儿童歌曲“Freewheelin”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-alice-cooper-2450600"><b>摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ ——爱丽丝·库珀</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>在充满活力的赛道上，爱丽丝和卡利科唱着<em>“我在我的新自行车上随心所欲/这是我喜欢的最好的事情/现在你可以自己随心所欲地骑车/在没有任何帮助的情况下踩得更快”，</em>描述了骑自行车的乐趣骑自行车，而 Slash 则演奏令人振奋的吉他独奏。</p><p> 《Freewheelin》收录在获得格莱美提名的儿童摇滚专辑《Solid Rock Revival》中。 Rock for Children 是一个音乐团体，由 Alice 和他的女儿以及 Sharon Aguilar-Kamide、Dana Kamide、Ms. Meka Nism、Recker Eans、Conrad Varela、John David Williams 和 Rubén Salas 组成。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="儿童摇滚 - Freewheelin’（壮举。Slash、Alice Cooper、Calico Cooper）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1H9AO4514wc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Solid Rock Revival》获得 2025 年格莱美奖最佳儿童音乐专辑提名，其中包括<a href="/artists/judgas-priest">Judas Priest</a>的<a href="/artists/rob-halford">Rob Halford</a> 、 <a href="/artists/run-dmc">Run DMC</a>的 Daryl “DMC” McDaniels 等。这张唱片的收益将捐献给 Cooper&#39;s<a href="https://arizonansforchildren.org/mentorportal/teen-center/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Solid Rock Teen Centers</a> ，这是一个为 12-20 岁青少年提供免费音乐、舞蹈、艺术等课外培训的非营利组织。</p><p>在谈到与<a href="https://www.azcentral.com/story/entertainment/music/2024/11/13/alice-cooper-grammy-nomination-best-childrens-album/76198520007/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>亚利桑那共和乐队</em></a>一起获得格莱美提名时，爱丽丝分享道：“对于爱丽丝·库珀来说，获得儿童音乐格莱美奖不是最疯狂的事情吗？”</p><p>他继续说道：“我认为这确实对[孩子们]说了些什么。我们有一张可以赢得格莱美奖的专辑……对于孩子们来说，看到成功的发生是一件非常酷的事情，最小的种子成长为那么大的东西。有时你为了乐趣而做的事情结果真的非常好。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DArU1_TOjty/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 5